{{Top|canon=Starshine Special}}
{{Image}}
'''"Starshine special"''' was a popular additive to [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] drinks in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] during the last decades of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. For the right wink, a patron in the [[Outlander Club/Legends|Outlander Club]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] could have it added to their cocktail. It may be related to or have similar strength as the [[Starshine Surprise]].

